            <p class="mb-4">Custom printing is most accessible when the design process is as simple as possible. For most people who order custom shirts, signs, or other products, the design is the hard part — not the production. Our design catalog removes the hardest part by giving you thousands of professionally designed starting points that cover every common custom print use case, in every style and aesthetic, across every product category we offer. The catalog turns "I don't know what design to use" into a solved problem.</p>
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Professional Quality Without Professional Design Fees</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Hiring a professional graphic designer for a one-time custom shirt or event banner is a significant investment that does not make financial sense for many individuals and small organizations. Design catalogs give you access to professional design quality without the professional design fee, because the template work has already been done. You pay for the production of your custom product, not for the design time — and the result is a professionally designed finished product at a fraction of the cost of a fully custom design project.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="mid">
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Covers Every Common Use Case</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Our catalog includes designs for family reunions, school events, church groups, sports teams, business promotions, birthday celebrations, bachelorette parties, fundraisers, professional uniforms, and dozens of other common custom print applications. Whatever your specific use case, there are almost certainly multiple templates in the catalog that fit it well. The catalog is organized by category and use case so you can navigate quickly to the designs most relevant to your project without browsing through thousands of unrelated templates.</p>
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">A Foundation for More Custom Work</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Many of our long-term clients started their relationship with Top 5 Percent by ordering a catalog-based design and then gradually developed more custom, original designs as their brand identity matured. The catalog serves as a starting point that gives new clients a low-risk, fast path to their first order, after which they develop a more specific creative vision based on their experience with the initial product. We welcome clients at every stage of their design journey and support them from first catalog order to fully custom original artwork.</p>
